---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { SITE, pairAlternates } from '@/lib/site';
---

<PageLayout
  title={`About | ${SITE.name}`}
  description="Yifang Dong — software engineer writing about craftsmanship, building software, and learning."
  lang="en"
  canonicalPath="/about/"
  alternates={pairAlternates('/about/', '/zh-cn/about/')}
>
  <article class="markdown">
    <h1>Hi there! I'm Yifang Dong.</h1>
    <p>
      I'm a software engineer who genuinely loves the art of programming. For me, code isn't just about
      making things work—it's about the challenge of solving problems within unique constraints and finding
      that perfect balance in technical trade-offs.
    </p>

    <h2>My Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a big believer in software craftsmanship. I focus on clean, maintainable, and efficient design
      because I think intentionality is what separates a good developer from a great one. Programming gives
      me a sense of creative freedom; it's a space where I can constantly experiment, learn, and push the
      boundaries of what's possible.
    </p>

    <h2>Why This Site?</h2>
    <p>I use this space as a digital notebook to document my journey. You'll find my thoughts on:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Building Software:</strong> Insights into architecture, design discussions, and coding
        patterns.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>The Craft:</strong> Reflections on professional growth and the day-to-day life of an
        engineer.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Continuous Learning:</strong> Lessons learned from the problems I've tackled and the
        systems I've helped build.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Ultimately, my goal is to keep refining my skills and contribute to impactful, well-crafted systems
      that make a difference.
    </p>

    <h2>A Note on Language</h2>
    <p>
      I write my posts in both English and Chinese. If you'd like
      to switch between them, just use the language link located in the footer.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/YifangDONG" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yifang-dong-dev" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://x.com/D_YIF" rel="noopener noreferrer">X / Twitter</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
